title: Justin Smith from Graf Orlock
itunes:title: Justin Smith from Graf Orlock
description:
We sit down with Justin Smith, the guitarist from Graf Orlock, vocalist/guitarist from Ghostlimb and guitarist for Dangers (that is a mouthful). We discuss growing up in Orange County, the REAL story behind Graf Orlock and why the director of HEAT pre-ordered a 7". 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
